every pot--even in private houses, as in the temple, shall be deemed
holy, so universal shall be the consecration of all things and persons
to Jehovah.

take of them--as readily as they would take of the pots of the temple
itself, whatever number they wanted for sacrifice.

no . . . Canaanite--no unclean or ungodly person ([Isa
